## One user collection [/users/{username}]

### Show one user [GET]

+ Parameters
    + username (text) - username of a user

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "id": 1,
            "firstname": "Test",
            "lastname": "Test",
            "username" : "test",
            "gender": 0,
            "email": "test@mail.ee",
            "password": "testtest"
        }

## User profile collection [/profiles/{user_id}]

### Show user's profile [GET]

+ Parameters
    + user_id (text) - id of a user
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "profile_id": 1,
            "user_id": 1,
            "location": "Narnia",
            "pic": "http://trialx.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/animals/Cabbagehead-3.jpg"
        }
        
### Create new profile [POST]

+ Parameters
    + user_id (text) - id of a user
    
+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "user_id": 5,
            "sports": "Korvpall",
            "level": "Kerge",
            "location": "Hogwarts",
            "pic": "http://trialx.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/04/animals/Cabbagehead-3.jpg"
        }
        
+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /profiles/5

    + Body

            {
                "user_id": 5,
                "sports": "Korvpall",
                "level": "Kerge",
                "location": "Hogwarts",
