            }

## Sports collection [/users/{user_id}/sports]

### Show all sports of a user [GET]

+ Parameters 
    + user_id (text) - id of a user
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "sports_id" : 1, 
                "user_id" : 1,
                "sports" : "Jalgpall",
                "level" : "Kerge"
            },
            {
                "sports_id" : 2, 
                "user_id" : 1, 
                "sports" : "Sulgpall",
                "level" : "Keskmine"
            }
        ]
        
### Add sports to a user [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
    
        {
            "user_id" : 1,
            "sports" : "Korvpall", 
            "level" : "Raske"
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /users/{user_id}/sports/2

    + Body

            {
                "sports_id" : 2,
                "user_id" : 1,
                "sports" : "Korvpall", 
                "level" : "Raske"
            }
        
