## Practice additional information collection [/practices/{practice_id}/additional]

### Show additional information of a practice [GET]

+ Parameters
    + practice_id (number) - id of a practice
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "practice_id": 1,
            "min": 3,
            "max": 15,
            "gender": 1
        }

### Create new additional information of a practice [POST]

+ Request (application/json)
        
        {
            "practice_id": 2,
            "min": 1,
            "max": 10,
            "gender": 0
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /practices/2/additional

    + Body

            {
                "practice_id": 2,
                "min": 1,
                "max": 10,
                "gender": 0
            }